291
00:13:01,080 --> 00:13:01,490
Hello.

292
00:13:01,510 --> 00:13:02,180
Oh my god.

293
00:13:02,720 --> 00:13:03,580
Ms. Gao.

294
00:13:03,840 --> 00:13:04,370
No need to get up!

295
00:13:04,390 --> 00:13:05,490
Is it really you?

296
00:13:05,750 --> 00:13:06,340
Yeah.

297
00:13:07,600 --> 00:13:09,100
After hearing your story,

298
00:13:09,120 --> 00:13:10,250
I had to come.

299
00:13:10,630 --> 00:13:12,460
You're so brave.

300
00:13:12,480 --> 00:13:15,490
"A mother's love makes her strong".

301
00:13:15,750 --> 00:13:18,340
You have embodied that.

302
00:13:22,080 --> 00:13:23,980
This must be Zhang Zhe?

303
00:13:24,390 --> 00:13:25,130
Hello, Ms Gao.

304
00:13:25,630 --> 00:13:26,370
Young man.

305
00:13:26,750 --> 00:13:29,490
You should take good care of your mom.

306
00:13:29,510 --> 00:13:31,100
I will. Thank you.

307
00:13:31,870 --> 00:13:32,940
I can't believe that

308
00:13:33,270 --> 00:13:35,180
