312
00:13:41,270 --> 00:13:42,820
The initial treatment didn't go well.

313
00:13:43,120 --> 00:13:44,300
Thanks to Dr. Zhou, I can.

314
00:13:44,320 --> 00:13:45,980
What is happening? Wang Yibo is here?

315
00:13:46,000 --> 00:13:47,490
Gao Yalan—Ms. Gao is inside.

316
00:13:47,510 --> 00:13:49,340
See how well I've recovered?

317
00:13:49,360 --> 00:13:50,530
Can't tell, right?

318
00:13:50,670 --> 00:13:51,850
Yes.

319
00:13:52,750 --> 00:13:54,940
I have just watched your show on TV

320
00:13:55,270 --> 00:13:56,700
last month.

321
00:13:56,720 --> 00:13:57,370
Really?

322
00:13:58,150 --> 00:13:58,730
Zhang Zhe.

323
00:13:58,750 --> 00:14:00,180
You like singing, too. Right?

324
00:14:00,750 --> 00:14:02,060
A pro is here.

325
00:14:02,390 --> 00:14:03,300
Don't flatter me.

326
00:14:03,840 --> 00:14:04,490
Ms. Gao.

327
00:14:05,000 --> 00:14:06,340
I've studied vocal music before.

328
00:14:06,360 --> 00:14:07,700
I can play guitar well.

329
00:14:07,720 --> 00:14:09,730
And I have also published several songs.

330
00:14:12,550 --> 00:14:13,130
Please get in.

331
00:14:13,150 --> 00:14:15,700
You've got potential. Relax.

332
00:14:15,910 --> 00:14:18,340
You can just leave medical issues to Dr. Zhou.

333
00:14:19,000 --> 00:14:20,060
As for your music career,

334
00:14:20,080 --> 00:14:21,700
you can come to me.

335
00:14:21,720 --> 00:14:22,890
Don't be shy.

336
00:14:23,670 --> 00:14:24,300
Thank you!

337
00:14:24,320 --> 00:14:25,250
Thank you, Ms. Gao.

338
00:14:25,270 --> 00:14:26,770
Never mind.

339
00:14:26,910 --> 00:14:27,610
Thank you!

340
00:14:29,670 --> 00:14:30,370
Thank you!

341
00:14:38,320 --> 00:14:40,130
Changing the fish tank water

342
00:14:40,150 --> 00:14:41,250
must be a hassle.

343
00:14:42,510 --> 00:14:44,770
I got no time for that.

344
00:14:45,510 --> 00:14:46,820
Qing is caring them all the time.

345
00:14:48,120 --> 00:14:48,850
They are lucky fish.

346
00:14:50,550 --> 00:14:52,890
I often get new ones

347
00:14:53,750 --> 00:14:56,490
from the market.

348
00:14:56,510 --> 00:14:57,700
There is always something new in the market.

349
00:14:58,440 --> 00:14:59,130
Look at this.

350
00:14:59,390 --> 00:15:00,940
that black one with red edges.

351
00:15:01,870 --> 00:15:03,130
It's always alone

352
00:15:03,750 --> 00:15:05,100
and doesn't vie for food.

353
00:15:05,320 --> 00:15:06,060
I just thought that

354
00:15:06,240 --> 00:15:07,700
it can't make it to this month.

355
00:15:08,080 --> 00:15:09,530
But it proves that I am wrong.

356
00:15:11,150 --> 00:15:12,820
Less eating guarantees longevity.

357
00:15:13,150 --> 00:15:15,340
Maybe it will live longer than others.

358
00:15:16,840 --> 00:15:18,340
Fish keeping is like parenting.

359
00:15:18,360 --> 00:15:20,890
It doesn't matter how you cure them,

360
00:15:22,320 --> 00:15:24,420
but how you prevent them from falling ill.

361
00:15:25,600 --> 00:15:26,730
This tank is pricey.

362
00:15:27,670 --> 00:15:29,980
It can't accommodate too many fish at a time.

363
00:15:30,120 --> 00:15:31,340
It can't contain too many big ones.

364
00:15:31,360 --> 00:15:33,940
The water temperature. flow and quality

365
00:15:33,960 --> 00:15:35,610
should all be well managed.

366
00:15:36,510 --> 00:15:38,300
You just said you are not interested in raising fish.

367
00:15:38,790 --> 00:15:40,180
But you know everything.

368
00:15:41,390 --> 00:15:42,530
I am indeed not interested,

369
00:15:42,550 --> 00:15:44,420
but that doesn't mean I have to stop getting to know them.

370
00:15:44,670 --> 00:15:45,220
Come.

371
00:15:45,480 --> 00:15:46,820
Let's have some tea.

372
00:15:47,600 --> 00:15:49,770
I'm planning to talk to you anyway.

373
00:15:50,600 --> 00:15:52,010
That robot is too large.

374
00:15:52,030 --> 00:15:53,770
You can't just

375
00:15:54,120 --> 00:15:55,370
always push it around the hospital.

376
00:15:55,670 --> 00:15:56,250
That's crazy.

377
00:15:56,270 --> 00:15:58,370
It looks like a Transformer set.

378
00:15:59,000 --> 00:16:00,250
Mr. Qin

379
00:16:00,510 --> 00:16:02,370
shouldn't just let you handle it alone.

380
00:16:02,600 --> 00:16:04,980
The 5G tele-operation is a big project.

381
00:16:05,000 --> 00:16:06,890
Everyone should do their part for it.

382
00:16:08,240 --> 00:16:10,730
Mr. Qin has already funded us.

383
00:16:11,240 --> 00:16:12,940
He shall not be bothered by these trivial things.

384
00:16:13,200 --> 00:16:14,580
Come on.

385
00:16:14,840 --> 00:16:15,890
We can just talk about it in the meeting.

386
00:16:16,840 --> 00:16:18,610
Black tea or Longjing tea?

387
00:16:19,510 --> 00:16:20,460
Whatever you get me.

388
00:16:20,480 --> 00:16:21,220
I' m both fine.

389
00:16:22,390 --> 00:16:24,220
Is the date scheduled?

390
00:16:24,630 --> 00:16:26,180
Please keep me informed.

391
00:16:26,600 --> 00:16:28,130
So I can send those young people

392
00:16:28,440 --> 00:16:29,370
to learn something.

393
00:16:29,390 --> 00:16:31,650
They are fooling around.

394
00:16:31,670 --> 00:16:33,100
They don't even know

395
00:16:33,240 --> 00:16:34,100
the current situation of the project.

396
00:16:34,120 --> 00:16:35,820
You are quite interested.

397
00:16:36,150 --> 00:16:38,130
I have to.

398
00:16:38,390 --> 00:16:39,850
The era we are living in

399
00:16:39,870 --> 00:16:40,820
is so horrible.

400
00:16:41,390 --> 00:16:43,370
New things keep coming.

401
00:16:43,390 --> 00:16:45,220
I'm so happy that you can be here.

402
00:16:45,240 --> 00:16:46,610
You have brought us a lot fresh ideas.

403
00:16:47,030 --> 00:16:48,530
Not flattery.

404
00:16:48,910 --> 00:16:49,890
I do think that

405
00:16:50,550 --> 00:16:52,650
the medicine aesthetics industry really needs people

406
00:16:52,670 --> 00:16:55,250
as visionary and ambitious as you.

407
00:16:55,870 --> 00:16:57,060
I do have a vision of

408
00:16:57,360 --> 00:16:59,370
how good your tea will be.

409
00:16:59,510 --> 00:17:00,180
Right?

410
00:17:00,960 --> 00:17:02,700
Ms. Li from Li Ge gave it to me.

411
00:17:03,510 --> 00:17:04,290
She told me that

412
00:17:04,310 --> 00:17:06,570
an entire tea hill can only

413
00:17:06,830 --> 00:17:08,530
produce a small bag of it.

414
00:17:08,550 --> 00:17:09,980
Take it if you like.

415
00:17:10,350 --> 00:17:11,180
I will ask her to get me more later.

416
00:17:11,200 --> 00:17:12,050
I appreciate it. But no.

417
00:17:12,270 --> 00:17:13,220
That's too good for me.

418
00:17:13,640 --> 00:17:14,730
Grape is enough for me.

419
00:17:14,750 --> 00:17:16,250
My biggest flaw I think

420
00:17:16,270 --> 00:17:18,220
is my crazy pursuit of talents.

421
00:17:18,240 --> 00:17:19,620
Since you have joined us,

422
00:17:20,000 --> 00:17:21,730
we have never talked.

423
00:17:21,960 --> 00:17:22,810
Today,

424
00:17:22,830 --> 00:17:23,900
I have to win you over.

425
00:17:25,270 --> 00:17:27,290
Training a doctor’s tough.

426
00:17:27,510 --> 00:17:29,460
You have to go through medical school, PhD,

427
00:17:29,480 --> 00:17:31,980
training, residency and a lot

428
00:17:32,160 --> 00:17:34,460
which will take at least 15 years.

429
00:17:35,030 --> 00:17:36,250
Not to mention talents like you,

430
00:17:36,270 --> 00:17:37,810
who have got this far

431
00:17:37,830 --> 00:17:39,090
by performing operations to gain reputation.

432
00:17:39,400 --> 00:17:40,660
That's really amazing.

433
00:17:42,920 --> 00:17:44,050
My duty

434
00:17:44,830 --> 00:17:46,770
is to make sure that

435
00:17:46,790 --> 00:17:48,730
every doctor here can fully exert their talent.

436
00:17:50,400 --> 00:17:51,770
Good to hear that.

437
00:17:52,310 --> 00:17:54,050
Then I shall tell you directly.

438
00:17:55,030 --> 00:17:55,980
I have met many obstacles

439
00:17:56,000 --> 00:17:57,900
in promoting the 5G tele-operation

440
00:17:57,920 --> 00:17:59,530
in our hospital.

441
00:17:59,880 --> 00:18:01,810
I don't have any other interests

442
00:18:01,830 --> 00:18:03,290
but a perfect operation.

443
00:18:03,830 --> 00:18:05,380
But recently I notice that

444
00:18:05,590 --> 00:18:06,810
there is something troublesome

445
00:18:07,550 --> 00:18:09,250
unrelated to surgery

446
00:18:09,270 --> 00:18:10,330
bothering me a lot.

447
00:18:10,550 --> 00:18:11,810
That's quite annoying.

448
00:18:16,920 --> 00:18:18,330
So I come to you today,

449
00:18:18,830 --> 00:18:20,420
hoping that you can support me.

450
00:18:21,160 --> 00:18:21,900
I understand.

451
00:18:22,720 --> 00:18:23,940
Then you shall get my support.

452
00:18:24,350 --> 00:18:25,090
That's great!

453
00:18:25,350 --> 00:18:26,980
But there is a string attached.

454
00:18:27,400 --> 00:18:28,660
You have to answer me a question.

455
00:18:28,920 --> 00:18:29,530
What's that?

456
00:18:30,030 --> 00:18:32,530
You had a stable job at the Third Hospital,

457
00:18:32,550 --> 00:18:33,660
and you are so excellent.

458
00:18:34,030 --> 00:18:35,380
Why did you choose us?

459
00:18:35,400 --> 00:18:36,570
Maybe it's because the salary,

460
00:18:37,550 --> 00:18:38,490
cute guys here,

461
00:18:38,750 --> 00:18:40,660
and the 5G tele-operation.

462
00:18:40,680 --> 00:18:41,620
So I am here.

463
00:18:43,790 --> 00:18:44,460
All right, it's the time.

464
00:18:44,880 --> 00:18:45,980
Time for surgery.

465
00:18:46,790 --> 00:18:48,290
Keep pushing for the project!

466
00:18:59,160 --> 00:19:00,050
Professor Chu.

467
00:19:00,640 --> 00:19:03,180
Dr. Zhou says you're her mentor,

468
00:19:03,880 --> 00:19:05,530
a legend in this field.

469
00:19:06,200 --> 00:19:08,140
I'm honored

470
00:19:08,350 --> 00:19:09,810
that you're treating me.

471
00:19:10,030 --> 00:19:10,980
Thank you.

472
00:19:11,200 --> 00:19:12,140
Don't believe them.

473
00:19:12,350 --> 00:19:13,700
This is just my job.

474
00:19:13,880 --> 00:19:15,290
I'm also a fan of yours.

475
00:19:15,480 --> 00:19:16,860
When HongKong was recovered in 1997,

476
00:19:16,880 --> 00:19:18,660
you performed at our military compound.

477
00:19:18,960 --> 00:19:20,460
We have taken a photo together.

478
00:19:21,750 --> 00:19:22,620
Really?

479
00:19:22,750 --> 00:19:24,250
You wouldn't remember.

480
00:19:25,240 --> 00:19:26,860
It was a long time ago.

481
00:19:26,880 --> 00:19:28,420
Times change.

482
00:19:29,000 --> 00:19:30,420
Relax.

483
00:19:30,720 --> 00:19:32,050
When I was young,

484
00:19:32,350 --> 00:19:33,900
I have won every award.

485
00:19:34,200 --> 00:19:37,810
But now,

486
00:19:38,240 --> 00:19:39,900
I was eliminated in two rounds on The Voice.

487
00:19:40,310 --> 00:19:42,220
I know it myself that

488
00:19:42,400 --> 00:19:44,490
I am just a stepping stone for kids.

489
00:19:45,000 --> 00:19:47,530
But I still can't accept it.

490
00:19:48,070 --> 00:19:49,620
All right, relax now.

491
00:19:50,720 --> 00:19:52,860
People nowadays have taste for art.

492
00:19:52,880 --> 00:19:54,090
They only care about appearance.

493
00:19:54,110 --> 00:19:55,860
"Countenance matters" as it's used

494
00:19:55,880 --> 00:19:57,180
in the catchy words today.

495
00:19:58,640 --> 00:20:00,250
People always say that,

496
00:20:01,590 --> 00:20:03,050
singer may get older,

497
00:20:03,070 --> 00:20:05,250
but the fans will always remain young.

498
00:20:05,440 --> 00:20:06,330
That's right.

499
00:20:07,310 --> 00:20:09,220
The same is true of my job.

500
00:20:09,240 --> 00:20:11,860
People aesthetics are evolving every year.

501
00:20:12,640 --> 00:20:14,050
If I were young ladies,

502
00:20:14,550 --> 00:20:16,570
I will also choose Zhou to perform operation on me.

503
00:20:17,750 --> 00:20:19,420
You really have a light heart.

504
00:20:19,920 --> 00:20:21,940
You have taught me a lesson.

505
00:20:21,960 --> 00:20:22,730
We should never

506
00:20:23,160 --> 00:20:24,860
take ourselves too seriously.

507
00:20:25,350 --> 00:20:26,770
When I just retired,

508
00:20:26,790 --> 00:20:27,940
I felt low as well.

509
00:20:28,440 --> 00:20:30,420
No matter how great you are,

510
00:20:30,440 --> 00:20:31,810
you are an ordinary person after all.

511
00:20:32,030 --> 00:20:33,490
The higher people place you,

512
00:20:33,510 --> 00:20:35,140
the more arrogant you will be.

513
00:20:35,440 --> 00:20:37,380
And when that happens, all you hear will be lies.

514
00:20:37,400 --> 00:20:39,010
You won't have any real friends.

515
00:20:39,350 --> 00:20:41,250
You will just live your life alone,

516
00:20:41,270 --> 00:20:43,050
like a statue.

517
00:20:43,310 --> 00:20:46,090
That kind of life is meaningless.

518
00:20:46,790 --> 00:20:47,940
Look at me now.

519
00:20:48,070 --> 00:20:49,940
Doing something

520
00:20:50,200 --> 00:20:51,660
within my capacity

521
00:20:51,880 --> 00:20:53,660
not only pleases you

522
00:20:53,680 --> 00:20:55,420
but also makes me happy.

523
00:20:57,350 --> 00:20:58,660
I really need to think about

524
00:20:59,400 --> 00:21:00,940
what you just said.

525
00:21:00,960 --> 00:21:01,730
Yeah, you can think about it now,

526
00:21:01,750 --> 00:21:03,810
but don't frown.

527
00:21:04,510 --> 00:21:06,490
Can I check it now?

528
00:21:06,510 --> 00:21:07,330
Here, the mirror.

529
00:21:07,550 --> 00:21:08,770
Well, let me see.

530
00:21:09,920 --> 00:21:11,250
Isn't that better now?

531
00:21:12,110 --> 00:21:14,010
Well. it really is.

532
00:21:14,030 --> 00:21:15,090
The hyaluronic acid

533
00:21:15,110 --> 00:21:17,180
is injected into the bone layer.

534
00:21:17,640 --> 00:21:18,660
You might feel odd

535
00:21:18,680 --> 00:21:20,180
at first,

536
00:21:20,480 --> 00:21:21,290
but that feeling will disappear

537
00:21:21,480 --> 00:21:24,140
in weeks.

538
00:21:24,270 --> 00:21:25,180
Well.

539
00:21:26,200 --> 00:21:29,050
A face lift would hurt more, right?

540
00:21:29,070 --> 00:21:30,620
Liu Xinfang is so amazing.

541
00:21:30,750 --> 00:21:32,180
She can even stand that pain.

542
00:21:32,960 --> 00:21:33,660
That's understandable.

543
00:21:33,880 --> 00:21:34,860
That's all for her son.

544
00:21:34,880 --> 00:21:36,620
Her son of my ass.

545
00:21:36,640 --> 00:21:38,420
That's not her son.

546
00:21:38,440 --> 00:21:39,770
It's just a show.

547
00:21:40,160 --> 00:21:41,420
They may fool you.

548
00:21:41,750 --> 00:21:43,330
But not me.

549
00:21:43,350 --> 00:21:45,180
I've been in this field too long. That's easy to identify.

550
00:21:48,270 --> 00:21:49,010
(Zhang Zhe.)

551
00:21:50,550 --> 00:21:51,900
(If you are watching this,)

552
00:21:52,880 --> 00:21:53,900
(please come home.)

553
00:21:55,790 --> 00:21:57,420
(I miss you a lot.)

554
00:21:59,240 --> 00:22:00,860
(Auntie, don't be sad.)

555
00:22:01,270 --> 00:22:02,530
(You will find your son someday.)

556
00:22:02,920 --> 00:22:05,330
(We will try our best to help you.)

557
00:22:06,960 --> 00:22:08,940
(Can you express your desire again?)

558
00:22:10,640 --> 00:22:11,730
(Regret now?)

559
00:22:12,160 --> 00:22:13,290
(That's too late.)

560
00:22:13,790 --> 00:22:14,700
(I'm wondering)

561
00:22:15,110 --> 00:22:17,050
(were they amicable like this)

562
00:22:17,550 --> 00:22:19,730
(when Zhang Zhe was still at home?)

563
00:22:20,880 --> 00:22:21,570
(That's right.)

564
00:22:21,680 --> 00:22:23,380
(The miserable deserve their misery.)

565
00:22:23,400 --> 00:22:25,050
(No parents are perfect.)

566
00:22:25,310 --> 00:22:26,860
(They are not saints. They will make mistakes.)

567
00:22:26,880 --> 00:22:28,250
(Even if they had disputes before,)

568
00:22:28,270 --> 00:22:29,860
(but they still love their kids.)

569
00:22:30,200 --> 00:22:31,530
(Don't be too hard on parents.)

570
00:22:31,550 --> 00:22:33,620
(You are family.)

571
00:22:38,960 --> 00:22:39,660
(Let's see.)

572
00:22:40,110 --> 00:22:42,050
(Will any normal person)

573
00:22:42,750 --> 00:22:44,940
(abandon their parents?)

574
00:22:50,030 --> 00:22:50,940
(From this day on,)

575
00:22:51,200 --> 00:22:53,180
(no more guitar.)

576
00:22:53,680 --> 00:22:55,050
